<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/756456-i-read-the-shadow-of-the-wind-and-i-ve">I read &quot;The Shadow of the Wind,&quot; and I&#39;ve tried reading this book, but can&#39;t seem to get through it. Is it possible to skip over this one and go onto the third book since this one is just a prequel?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_756456'><a id="like_count_community_question_756456" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/756456?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F4912857-the-angel-s-game">like</a></span>

