        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3524347115" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5128310808086774202">Back to the Cemetery of the Forgotten Books. We are transported back to again Barcelona, the perfect setting for this gothic tale.<br/>This is a captivating story by Carlos Ruiz Zafron. It is filled with mystery and intrigue and paranormal. Just when you think you know how the plot is going, BAM she get a big surprise. It is eloquently written with many twists and turns.<br/>If you like creepy old mansions and hidden secrets and things that are not what they seem to be. You will love this novel.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


